This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new optimization method for machine learning models. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with automated learning rate selection. Additionally, the paper mentions computer vision (cs.CV) as a potential application of the proposed method. The use of stochastic gradient descent (SGD) also suggests that it could belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
